data.title: Vivica A. Fox reignited demand for Quentin Tarantino’s “Kill Bill Vol. 3” in July after sharing that she’d love to see Zendaya take on the...
data.meta_description:
26K likes, 167 comments - indiewire on September 8, 2020: "Vivica A. Fox reignited demand for Quentin Tarantino’s “Kill Bill Vol. 3” in July after sharing that she’d love to see Zendaya take on the role of Vernita Green’s daughter. Her fan casting idea made its way to Zendaya herself, who was quite appreciative of the shout out.⁠
⁠
"I was quite honored that she would say that,” Zendaya said. “Obviously she’s incredible and I’m very flattered that she would think of me. You know, it’s just an idea. The internet kinda takes things and run with it.” Read more at the link in bio.⁠
––⁠
#killbill #zendaya #vivicaafox #quentintarantino #film".
